title: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight and map rules
description: Exception is thrown when exporting data from the attached report.
OB: When exporting data from a table in the report that contains a group row with a highlight rule and a map rule, an exception is thrown.
EB: No exception should be thrown when exporting data from a table with highlight and map rules.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Open the attached report. 2. Add a table with a group row, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row. 3. Preview the report. 4. Attempt to export the data from the table. Ensure that no exception is thrown.
